'''Brega Marketing Company''' ([[Arabic]]:  <U+0634><U+0631><U+0643><U+0629> <U+0627><U+0644><U+0628><U+0631><U+064A><U+0642><U+0629> <U+0644><U+062A><U+0633><U+0648><U+064A><U+0642> <U+0627><U+0644><U+0646><U+0641><U+0637> ) is a [[Libyan]] national company owned by the Libyan [[National Oil Corporation]]. Its main activities are marketing oil and related products. The company was established in [[1974]].

